{"tid":879026,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"撫摸兔仔很重要! 增加自尊心! 🐰🌟","createTime":"2018-10-27T15:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T06:34:24.000Z","uid":197098,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15cf911cfdc6894521639ccc2a0c0cc169ba44f7","tid":879026,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔子背後來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常的，無論是雌性騎着雄性或兩隻同性別的騎着大家。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=fce7614c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔仔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔仔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。大家可以看我寫兔子驚慌的post) 以下video 是主人要求兔仔groom 主人的例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=be05d161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>有趣影片:</em></span> 兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d5afebff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a> <br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔子的頸上來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=711427b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>資訊來源: <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=cd6aeb0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a> (頭3個chapters)</strong>"},{"pid":"2106f4138cbc91856165f3a595b9d95dd76139b3","tid":879026,"uid":127929,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNxNzVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNxNzVs.png&h=792cb627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f8ceb5d8f98789223adafa2f5095068342969b","tid":879026,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"1247e301371c2c45387c5c0ef5226e09aa1141c9","tid":879026,"uid":174578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"唔好宣傳兔協 is ok"},{"pid":"03f1e90a6ac857dc2d982269d5851f0f74c67e16","tid":879026,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2106f4138cbc91856165f3a595b9d95dd76139b3","tid":879026,"uid":127929,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNxNzVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNxNzVs.png&h=792cb627&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as